Game Day: Tuesdays and Thursday

Game Times

Teams will play once a week on Tuesdays or Thursdays.

By registering, you are committing to the times listed for the league. Schedule requests can be made, but are not guaranteed.

season_details:
Game Times

Teams will play once a week on Mondays
Games are played between 8pm and 10pm and last 60 minutes
Off Dates: 5/26
Game Format
Pickleball Rules
League will be played on Pickleball Courts (painted lines & nets on site)
Recreational Doubles League (self-ref)
Best out of 5 games played within a 60 minute time frame, whichever comes first (minimum of 2 players required to start the game)
Points are scored only by the serving team
6 weeks of regular season games (play to 11, win by 2)
Equipment: players must bring their own paddles
Maximum roster size is 6. Additional players can be added for $35/person by sending us a customer service ticket
All individuals and small groups will be placed on a team with a maximum of 6 players on the roster. Two players from one team will be on the court at one time and will play two players from the opposing team. Teams with more than two players can choose to alternate games or rotate in on a serve. Your team will have 60 minutes for a match to play up to 5 games and the winner will be best out of 5. If there is a winner before the allotted time is up, the team can scrimmage for the remaining time, ensuring you still have 60 minutes to play.

You have two options for registration:

You can register as a team captain/full team and decide how many players you would like on your team (2 min, 6 max). This also will ensure you will be registered at the same time.
You can register as an individual/small group, and you will be placed on a team with other individuals and/or small groups. Each of these teams will have up to 6 players depending on the registration.

season_details:
2 DIVISION FOR THIS LEAGUE


This is 5 v 5 coed beach volleyball.

Games will be between 1pm & 4pm every Sunday.
SIGN UP EARLY AND SAVE: Many CLUBWAKA Kickball Leagues offer tiered pricing, meaning the earlier you sign up, the more you can save! So what are you waiting for? Register today and buy yourself a beer or two with the savings!
No team? No Problem! With CLUBWAKA, you don't need to round up a full team to join the fun. CLUBWAKA accepts free agents and small groups and we'll match you up with a team that fits your competitive and social preferences!
The minimum for a team is 7 registered players (min. of 3 of each gender). Max amount of registered players on a team is 12 players. 2 of each gender must be represented each week to avoid forfeit.
2 DIVISION FOR THIS LEAGUE: SOCIAL & COMPETITIVE. Social is more for beginner/intermediate players, who like to have fun and not take the game as seriously. Competitive consists of more intermediate/advanced players, who also like to have fun but may take the game more seriously  


KEY DATES**

5/25/25 - LAST DAY FOR EARLY BIRD REGISTRATION PRICES

6/8/25 - FREE Open Play - Come out to learn the rules, get some practice in or find a teammate!

6/8/25 - LAST DAY FOR REGULAR REGISTRATION PRICES

6/9/25 - Team Registration Deadline - All registrations after this date will be free agents placed on existing teams

7/6/25 - No Games - Forth of July Holiday Weekend

7/13/25 - Week 4

8/10/25 - Week 8 - Playoffs/Championships

**STAY HOME IF YOU ARE SICK!!!**

season_details:
CLUBWAKA Kickball is your ultimate ticket to meeting awesome new people! Whether you are new to LA, want to broaden your social circle, or simply throw in some fun into your week, guess what? CLUBWAKA Kickball has got you covered!

Season Starts Wednesday, June 4
Free, Open-Kick is Wednesday, May 28 at 7:30pm. Come see what we are all about. This is a great way for new players, and for those on the fence about wanting to join, to get to know the game and meet other players. 
Game Time: Games will be between 7:30pm and 10pm every Wednesday.
Get Social at the Bar: After the games, CLUBWAKA Kickballers will head over to the bar for some Team Social Games. It's the perfect opportunity to mix, mingle, and enjoy some food and drink specials.
Register Today: Once we reach league capacity, registration will close. This League offers tiered pricing, meaning the earlier you sign up, the more you can save! So what are you waiting for? Register today!
All Players Welcome: No team? No Problem! With CLUBWAKA, you don't need to round up a full team to join the fun. CLUBWAKA accepts free agents and small groups and we'll match you up with a team that fits your competitive and social preferences!
Specific League Rules

Depending on size of rosters, play may be 11 vs 11 or 10 vs 10. The combination of male to female ratio may change as well due to amount of people who register. 

The minimum that must be ready to play at game time is 8 (4 male, 4 female).     
                               
        

RESOURCES

CLUBWAKA Kickball Rules

How It Works

CLUBWAKA Kickball League Policies
League Facebook Group


STAFF CONTACTS
League & Social Manager: Shawn Sparks, ssparks@clubwaka.com 
General Manager: Jennifer Pesavento, doctorj@clubwaka.com


KEY DATES*

5/14/25 - Last Date to get Early Bird Pricing

5/28/25- FREE Open Play - Come out to learn the rules, get some practice or find a teammate!

5/29/25 - Team Registration Deadline - All registrations after this date will be free agents placed on existing teams

4v4 Coed Beach Volleyball League in Belmont Shore

9am-1pm Saturday Mornings in Belmont Shore (Granada Beach)

The Summer 2025 Season begins Saturday May 31st!


- Advanced Coaching Sessions available

- 7 Weeks of (2) 1 Hour Matches (Double Headers) including Playoffs

- Games played Saturday Mornings (9am- 1pm) in Belmont Shore

- 4v4 Adult Coed (3-4 players on the court at a time - at least 1 female player)

- Intermediate & Beginner Divisions with Set Teams

- Sign up as an Individual Player, Small Group, or a Team (min 6 players/team)

- Registration Fee: $95 per player before May 23rd

- OPTIONAL Dri-Fit Team Shirts ($20 additional) ADD-ON PURCHASE at the end of registration

- Sponsor Bar Discounts, Prizes, Giveaways, New Friends, and More!
